{"tid":887374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"藍潔瑛暴斃！","createTime":"2018-11-03T00:42:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-03T03:52:58.000Z","uid":83052,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"21b4d2f63135df19ddb212c40060e76c4928d5d9","tid":887374,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T00:42:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181103/1459444\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181103%2F1459444&d=uAEzzDC6Oflb2NFRLFWiNQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=d398da87\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181103%2F1459444&h=571ac8ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181103/1459444</a><br />\n香港藝人藍潔瑛，周六（3日）凌晨驚傳暴斃。香港《蘋果日報》報導，一名54歲的雷姓女子於周六凌晨零時許報警，指她的55歲藍姓女友人，住家沒有人應門，且傳出異味及噪音。消防破門後，發現女屋主倒臥地上，證實死亡。初步調查，沒有他殺等可疑跡象，把案件列為「發現屍體」處理，死因有待驗屍後確認。鄰居透露，死者為前無綫（TVB）藝員藍潔瑛。《蘋果》記者到場時，發現警方已將藍潔瑛住家封鎖，屋內仍傳出惡臭。"},{"pid":"5801834259a18d0eae1ec42d1543876b3788cd26","tid":887374,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T00:47:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e1b6ce14fe3005d07b979e8def9e0590204b54","tid":887374,"uid":91156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T00:54:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1249e93e460468cca63aec20d9f3b3ec7f42d1a","tid":887374,"uid":3399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T00:55:36.000Z","msg":"點解會有噪音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1616a616cd222e354a2fee2f476b42b14b4e8e25","tid":887374,"uid":100016,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T00:55:48.000Z","msg":"依家開post有積分？出邊十鳩幾個post仲開，搏乜？"},{"pid":"3e07163112a125e05408498d67f9215eb9b54679","tid":887374,"uid":80072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1249e93e460468cca63aec20d9f